{"tid":1946241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府禁四人以上聚會　林鄭承認這人數限制並無科學基礎","createTime":"2020-03-27T13:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T13:53:18.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ead4ffb9950d4161093ec58e2bbe2a45ceb9eb7b","tid":1946241,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:15:08.000Z","msg":"#港聞 政府因應疫情再公布一系列防疫措施，包括周日零時起禁止四人以上在公眾地方聚會，以減少人與人之間的接觸，工作間、婚禮喪禮等可豁免，措施為期十四天。行政長官林鄭月娥希望全港巿民可以自律，如非必要不要外出，為香港打贏這仗抗疫戰。 (3/27/21:08)"},{"pid":"35fcef8e87ee4dfe68732589f5c7854aa7065a78","tid":1946241,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385851&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=7af326ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385851&h=e6530821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385851</a>"},{"pid":"fe7cdfed770f5e30e6c268113d65c9978e8c1059","tid":1946241,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:16:06.000Z","msg":"工就要繼續返架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb153b478cab03d10d4247156e2dc0267b9d060d","tid":1946241,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為何要訂於四人以上，林鄭月娥承認並無科學基礎。林鄭月娥強調是基於公共衞生情況，提出嚴苛的措施，承認未必有足夠人手執法，但希望巿民可以自律。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n相關規例周日零時起生效，有效期14日。違例者定額罰款2000元，或最高罰款25000元、監禁六個月。"},{"pid":"d4f345f5804c6abc7467ab52d68c458afb2e0b89","tid":1946241,"uid":70786,"like":